You should probably ask these questions in an Android forum as I don't see any way to do this from inside a browser.<br /><br />Your safest bet would be reacting gracefully when the device leaves standby (i.e. if GPS suddenly becomes unavailable, just pause further processing until it is available).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1562">Alan</a> — Mon Jan 03, 2011 5:59 am</p><hr />
